com.uvce.cse.searchiot.encodeont.util

Class JenaUtils

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.uvce.cse.searchiot.encodeont.util.JenaUtils
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    OntologyDetails

    public class JenaUtils
extends Object
    Utility class to deal with the Ontology using Jena library. Reads an RDF/XML OWL file into in-memory model and prints it. Supports querying of the ontology through SPARQL end-points.
    Version:
    3.0
    Author:
    Santosh Pattar, Dwaraka Kulkarni
